Azure Container Apps is a serverless platform for running containerized applications and microservices on top of Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)â€”without having to manage the underlying Kubernetes infrastructure.

ğŸš€ What You Can Do with Azure Container Apps
âœ… Deploy microservices and APIs
âœ… Run background tasks & event-driven apps
âœ… Host scalable HTTP apps
